</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_432" id="215v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_432_r1l12">Biſchofen cʒu Meincʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_432_r1l13"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvılhelm Mendel <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_432_r1l14"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen gen franckfürt kümt cʒu <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> tage </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_432_r1l15">mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den von hanaw / Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> Ob derſelb vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_432_r1l16">Ratgeſell ewr gnad <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> icht anrüffen vvurd daʒ Jr Jm <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_432_r1l17">ewr fürdrung vnd hılffe gnediglich beweiſen wollet / Als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_432_r1l18">vnd das etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_432" id="215v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bischofen czu Meincz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als Wilhelm Mendel,
                            <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesell,
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        wegen gen Franckfürt kümt czu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tage mit
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den
                        von Hanaw, also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob derselb unser ratgesell
                        ewr gnad <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> icht anrüffen wurd, daz ir im
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr fürdrung und hilffe gnediglich
                        beweisen wollet. Als etc. Und das etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
